#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/3.0/guides/vertx.adoc:154
msgid "In the `src/main/resource` directory, create a `lorem.txt` file with the following content:"
msgstr "在 `src/main/resource` 目录中，创建一个包含以下内容的 `lorem.txt` 文件:"

